    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "I can finally replicate it (apparently only happened on a UMD build): \r\n\r\n```\r\nsrc/instantsearch.umd.js → dist/vue-instantsearch.js...\r\n[!] Error: 'EventEmitter' is not exported by node_modules/instantsearch.js/node_modules/events/events.js\r\nhttps://github.com/rollup/rollup/wiki/Troubleshooting#name-is-not-exported-by-module\r\nnode_modules/instantsearch.js/es/lib/InstantSearch.js (19:9)\r\n17: import union from 'lodash/union';\r\n18: import isPlainObject from 'lodash/isPlainObject';\r\n19: import { EventEmitter } from 'events';\r\n             ^\r\n20: import urlSyncWidget from './url-sync.js';\r\n21: import version from './version.js';\r\n```\r\n\r\nMade a PR too",
